Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.18,0:01:19.00,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}ただ刷り込まれたビジョン
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.22,0:01:22.60,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}無限遠点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.92,0:01:26.96,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}価値観を今
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.30,0:01:30.30,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}上書きする　変哲の無い宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.90,0:01:35.88,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}傲慢な神は目に映らない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.32,0:01:40.56,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}光速度で支配続けるならば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.78,0:01:45.52,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}僕は　僕だけは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.00,0:01:48.94,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}奇跡的で致命的な
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.98,0:01:52.46,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}マイノリティでいい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.80,0:01:53.90,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}I can fly──
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.94,0:01:56.62,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}あの瞬間、あの場面が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.64,0:01:59.32,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}キミにとって特別なら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.80,0:02:04.54,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}過去は離れて行くものなんかじゃなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.62,0:02:07.38,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}傷つく事の痛みより
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.38,0:02:10.12,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}大事なシーン　その全ての
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.20,0:02:15.20,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}ヒカリが今ゼロを生む
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.58,0:02:17.90,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}There is no god.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.16,0:02:21.00,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Wonderful new world.
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,---------------OPCN---------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.78,0:01:12.94,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}如果当今的天地并非现实
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.18,0:01:19.00,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}仅仅只是一个虚妄的掩饰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.22,0:01:22.60,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}无限远方那一点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.92,0:01:26.96,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}价值观逐渐畸变
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.30,0:01:30.30,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}逐步重建 不起涟漪宇宙间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.90,0:01:35.88,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}各路诸神心傲慢 藐视万物的空间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.32,0:01:40.56,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}仍以为光速 还能支配到宇宙天边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.78,0:01:45.52,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}对是我 只有我一个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.00,0:01:48.94,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}是极其罕见的致命异类之种
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.98,0:01:52.46,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}即将燎遍禁锢的天地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.80,0:01:53.90,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}自由翱翔──
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.94,0:01:56.62,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}还是那个瞬间 还是那些画面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.64,0:01:59.32,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}还是那些留恋 留在你的心间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.80,0:02:04.54,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}过去的那些琐事决未从此消失 也未曾远逝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.62,0:02:07.38,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}过去那些伤痛 再也不要提及
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.38,0:02:10.12,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}回忆那些留恋 是你成长阶梯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.20,0:02:15.20,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}用回忆的光将零之门 开启
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.58,0:02:17.90,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}从此再无神明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.16,0:02:21.00,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}欢迎美丽新世界
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,---------------EDJP---------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.50,0:22:13.14,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Come to me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.60,0:22:16.26,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Embrace my tears
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.90,0:22:22.74,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Let me guide you down into my soul
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.04,0:22:28.92,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}And let us pray for the world to realize
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.46,0:22:31.34,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}There is peace
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.70,0:22:35.52,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}The truth within us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.78,0:22:38.62,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Emptiness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.82,0:22:41.97,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Erodes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.10,0:22:47.86,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Cuz you're free from pain and sorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.40,0:22:54.36,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Future is just too bright to show you ways
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.52,0:22:56.52,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Wake up now
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.66,0:23:00.66,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}It's time to lead new souls
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.84,0:23:07.68,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Orbit of photon and universe
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.20,0:23:13.80,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}I am just the part of its plan
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.50,0:23:20.58,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}目には見えない歪んだ空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.80,0:23:28.20,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}人は何処へと歩いていくの？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.36,0:23:32.78,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}The last game
